node.title: Two hunters missing for three days in Fiordland found
node.description: The hunters walked out of the bush and are now being assessed by doctors.
node.content:
["Two hunters who have been missing in Fiordland since Saturday have been found.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123rf\n
", "The pair were found walking out of the bush near Lilliburn Valley Road.", "The police say they are being flown to Southland Hospital to be assessed as a precaution.", "They were reported overdue by fellow hunters on Sunday afternoon.", "Police said yesterday the pair were ill-equipped for a night out in the bush.", "Police Search and Rescue personnel, LandSAR, Amateur Radio Emergency Communications (AREC) personnel and search dogs were sent to the search area."]
